Jack Baxley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Baxley 0 Jack Baxley (born Andrew Jackson Baxley; July 4, 1884 – December 10, 1950) was an American character actor of the 1930s and 1940s. He appeared in over 100 films over his career, many in unnamed, un-credited roles. Occasionally he would receive small, named roles, and rarely a featured role.
